annotations.text: Official Journal of the European Union

annotations.label: Text
annotations.text: Calculation of capping of harmonised value added tax (VAT) bases pursuant to Article 2(1)(c) of Decision 2000/597/EC, Euratom
annotations.translation: 根据第 2000/597/EC 号决定第 2(1)(c) 条计算统一增值税 (VAT) 基数上限，欧洲原子能共同体

annotations.label: Table cell
annotations.text: 1% of reduced non capped VAT base (¹)
annotations.translation: 减少的无上限增值税基数的 1% (¹)

annotations.label: Table cell
annotations.text: 1% of reduced gross national income multiplied by capping rate t
annotations.translation: 减少的国民总收入的 1% 乘以上限率 t

annotations.label: Table cell
annotations.translation: 减少的增值税基数上限的 1%  (³)，(⁴)

annotations.label: Table cell
annotations.text: Member States whose VAT base is capped
annotations.translation: 有增值税基数上限的成员国

annotations.label: Footnote
annotations.text: (¹) The VAT bases of the ten new Member States have been reduced by one third to limit their contributions in view of the fact that the Accession Treaty took effect on 1 May 2004.
annotations.translation: (¹) 鉴于《加入条约》于 2004 年 5 月 1 日生效，十个新成员国的增值税基数已减去三分之一，以限制其缴款额。

annotations.label: Footnote
annotations.text: (²) The GNI bases of the ten new Member States have been reduced by one third to limit their contributions in view of the fact that the Accession Treaty took effect on 1 May 2004.
annotations.translation: (²) 鉴于《加入条约》于 2004 年 5 月 1 日生效，十个新成员国的国民总收入基数已减去三分之一，以限制其缴款额。

annotations.label: Footnote
annotations.text: (³) As with the GNI, a reduction of one third has been applied to the VAT bases of the new Member States to take account of the fact that the Accession Treaty took effect on 1 May 2004.
annotations.translation: (³) 鉴于《加入条约》于 2004 年 5 月 1 日生效，同国民总收入，新成员国的增值税基数已减去三分之一。

annotations.label: Footnote
annotations.text: (⁴) The base to be used does not exceed 50% of GNI.
annotations.translation: (⁴) 拟使用的基数不超过国民总收入的 50%。
